  <answer><![CDATA[<div class="c-page-content">
<p>Top walking routes near <a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva">Selva</a> include the Panascharte to Seceda, an easy to moderate 8km hike offering spectacular views of the Odle peaks from the summit of Seceda, accessible via cable car from Ortisei. Another great choice is the 7km hike up Pic Mountain for 360-degree views of Val Gardena, starting from San Cristina. For a more challenging experience, the 17km trek around the Sassolungo group begins at the Ciampinoi lift, featuring breathtaking landscapes and views over Seiser Alm.</p>
